alties Ltd is an intermediate precious metal royalty company that holds a North American focused portfolio of over 135 royalties, streams and precious metal offtakes. Osisko&#8217;s portfolio is anchored by its 5% NSR royalty on the Canadian Malartic Mine, which is the largest gold mine in Canada. Osisko also owns a portfolio of publicly held resource companies, including a 32.7% interest in Barkerville Gold Mines Ltd., a 16.6% interest in Osisko Mining Inc., an 18.8% interest in Victoria Gold Corp. and a 19.9% interest in Falco Resources Ltd.</p>   <p align=\"justify\">Osisko&#8217;s head office is located at 1100 Avenue des Canadiens-de Montr&#233;al, Suite 300, Montr&#233;al, Qu&#233;bec, H3B&#160;2S2.</p>   <p><strong>For further information, please contact Osisko Gold Royalties Ltd:</strong></p>   <p>Joseph de la Plante<br >Vice President, Corporate Development<br >Tel. (514) 940-0670<br >jdelaplante@osiskogr.com</p> </p><p ></p></body></html>\n</TEXT>\n</DOCUMENT>\n"
